SUMMARY:VOIVOD (can) + POISON RUIN (usa) + PRYNE (aut) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Arena
DESCRIPTION: | Arena Wien - Große Halle | Spanning more than 40 years and 15 studio albums\, five official lineups\, countless tours\, creative shifts\, changing tides\, road accidents and unspeakable tragedies\, Voivod\, born in Jonquière\, Quebec\, has persevered and gathered hordes of dedicated followers for one of the most fascinating rides in metal’s storied and ever-growing history. The marking of four decades as a unique and utterly creative metal institution finds Voivod riding a crest of adulation. They survived the fickle whims of music trends that didn’t always welcome them\; they survived a road accident that almost killed bassist/vocalist Eric Forrest\; they even narrowly survived total collapse\, with the unthinkable\, premature death of guitarist\, founding member\, and spiritual center\, Denis “Piggy” D’amour. But here they are\, claiming their stake on this ravaged planet. The entity is as strong and stable as it’s been since the band was founded 40 years ago. Recent artistic triumphs of The Wake and Synchro Anarchy have proven this. And just like they always have\, once the Morgöth Tales have been told\, they will turn the corner into 2026concentrating only on the future… https://www.voivod.com/  Poison Ruin Anarcho Punk/Death Rock/Post Punk/Dungeon Synth aus Philadelphia\, USA https://poisonruin.bandcamp.com/  Pryne By the power of friendship and the shared love for Mastodon & Wheeler Walker Jr.\, PRYNE was forged in 2021. Since then\, the Austrian Progressive Metal ensemble has been leaf-blowing their signature composite of fierce metal guitars and divinely polyphonic vocals to the people. https://pryne.bandcamp.com/  Vorverkauf Arena Shop € 32\,- (+ € 3\,50\,- Fee)  Abendkassa tba. 
URL:https://arena.wien/Home/Programm-Detail/concert-id/48491
